title: WTB: Circa 1908 Chicago Baseball Stadium RPPCs by Schumann Studios
author: patricka

posts.post_title: WTB: Circa 1908 Chicago Baseball Stadium RPPCs by Schumann Studios
posts.post_content: Looking for West Side Park and South Side Park RPPCs by Schumann Studios of Chicago.  There are 3 or 4 views of each of these stadiums that were commercially produced and include both interior and exterior views.  Please PM if you have any for sale.  Aggressive prices paid.
